verbose_text: The levels of miR-523-3p, miR-30a-3p and miR-16-5p were significantly higher in the plasma from pregnant women with fetal macrosomia, while no significant differences were detected in the expression levels of miR-181a-5p, miR-661, miR125a and miR-451a.
